title: question about victorus skin reward s6
body: hi im gold in rank 3v3s and i was just wondering if i will get the victorious at the end of the season and yes i have won more then 10 games wqith the team

replies.body: I don't have any information on ranked rewards for 2016.  Rewards any any ranked stuff will be posted on our [News](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) page.  Bookmark it to stay updated!
